1.01	Wig_in_a_Box_(song)	Hedwig and the Angry Inch Original Cast Album	Hedwig and the Angry Inch is a 2001 American musical film based on the stage musical of the same title about a fictional rock and roll band fronted by an East German transgendered singer. Hedwig is portrayed by John Cameron Mitchell, and the music and lyrics are by Stephen Trask. The musical has gathered a devoted cult following similar to that of The Rocky Horror Picture Show.	
